                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[27.05.2009]</p>
                <p>Animal welfare: The Norwegian Minister of Agriculture and Food, Mr Lars Peder Brekk, keep on working against the European Union in the question of animal slaughter anestetics. Brekk wants the union to acknowledge the countries' supremacy in deciding over this matter. -We must not reverse the ongoing work for animal welfare, says Brekk in a letter to five ministers of agriculture. </p>
                
                
